title: Hernán Williams
text: Hernán Williams (born 30 December 1985) is an Argentine <a href="cricket">cricket</a>er. He played in the <a href="2013%20ICC%20World%20Cricket%20League%20Division%20Six">2013 ICC World Cricket League Division Six</a> tournament. He was part of Argentina's squad for the <a href="2007%20ICC%20World%20Cricket%20League%20Division%20Two">2007 ICC World Cricket League Division Two</a> tournament in <a href="Windhoek">Windhoek</a>, Namibia, where he made his <a href="List%20A%20cricket">List A</a> debut.
